data.description: Great home, great neighborhood, 5 Bedroom with possibility for BR 6 in Basement! BRAND NEW Roof and Exterior Paint! The cathedral ceilings compliment the warm ambiance of the front living room. Enjoy the impressive kitchen with generous counter space, cabinetry and all appliances. The kitchen opens to the large family room. Walk out to the low maintenance backyard with turf, custom edging, large patio and mature landscaping. The study/bedroom with an adjacent bath compliments the main level. 4 additional bedrooms and 2 baths complete the upper level. The basement is finished with a family room/possible bedroom and bathroom. Garage has lots of possibilities with heater. Award winning Cherry Creek Schools. Close to shopping, entertainment venues, and easy commute to DIA, and Anschutz Medical Campus.
